data.description: This stunning, desirable model called Italian Villa offers a perfect blend of modern comfort and convenient location. This residence has 3 bedrooms and two-and-a-half baths, 3 car tandem garage within a spacious 2,257 square feet of living space. Built in 2020, this home features a Lots of upgrades that enhance both its aesthetics and functionality.    You're immediately greeted by an open floor plan that creates a sense of airiness and connectedness. The heart of this home is the beautifully appointed kitchen, featuring quartz countertops and white cabinets, stainless steel  appliances, eating bar dining, butlers pantry that not only add elegance but also provide durability for daily use. The kitchen is perfect for both the aspiring home chefs and for those who enjoy entertaining, with its generous counter space and sleek design.    Notable features of this residence are the solar panels,  built in office, Tankless water heater, remodeled hallway bath, which has been transformed into a stunning tile shower with beautiful fixtures, adding a touch of luxury to your daily routine.    The home also boasts a California room, which is an inviting outdoor space that seamlessly connects with the interior. It's an ideal spot for enjoying the California climate and hosting gatherings
